use' ./lang.af
use' ./time.af

\ ## Portable operating-system interfaces
\
\ POSIX process, identity, credential, and config decls from `<unistd.h>`.
\ Constant values and scalar ABI assumptions come from macOS 15.5.
\ Other targets may require different values and sizes.

