\ ## Signals
\
\ Signal numbers and structure layouts below are Darwin ABI choices. Signal
\ numbers are not portable constants; callers targeting another OS need its
\ own values. `Sigaction`, `Siginfo`, and `Sigstack` are passed by address.

U32 int: Sigset

